text: Salome Samadashvili (; born 2 April 1976) is a Georgian politician who is a United National Movement Member of the Parliament of Georgia. She was member of Parliament of Georgia three times (2004, 2016, 2020). ==References== Category:1983 births Category:Members of the Parliament of Georgia Category:United National Movement (Georgia) politicians Category:Living people
title: Salome Samadashvili
